<section class="greeting">
  <div class="title">INVITATION</div>
  <div class="message">
    <p>
      <span class="highlight"><b>민</b></span>들레처럼 고운 인연이 피어나<br />
      <span class="highlight"><b>섭</b></span>리처럼 자연스레 하나 되어<br />
      <span class="highlight"><b>다</b></span>가오는 모든 날을 함께 걸으며<br />
      <span class="highlight"><b>강</b></span>물처럼 흐르는 사랑으로 살겠습니다.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="parents">
    <div class="parent-line">
      <span class="parent-name">김병걸</span> · <span class="parent-name"
        >이경남</span
      >
      <span class="relation">의 장남</span>
      <span class="child-name">김민섭</span>
    </div>
    <div class="parent-line">
      <span class="parent-name">이용우</span> · <span class="parent-name"
        >박영자</span
      >
      <span class="relation">의 차녀</span>
      <span class="child-name">이다강</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .greeting {
    padding: calc(var(--section-padding-y) * 0.75) var(--section-padding-x)
      var(--section-padding-y);
    text-align: center;
    background: #fff;
  }

  .title {
    color: #9b785c;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .message {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 2.3;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .message p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .parents {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 2;
  }

  .parent-line {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .parent-name {
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .relation {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0 5px;
  }

  .child-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-left: 5px;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: #9b6437;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
